p: In addition, PQR also contains vitamins A, B, B2, B6 ( Chen and Cui, 2002), superoxide dismutase (SOD), peroxidase (POD), esterase (ES) ( Wu and Lin, 1991), nitrate reductase (NR), catalase (CAT), polyphenol oxidase (PPO), ascorbate peroxidase (APX) ( Wang S. et al., 2016), crude protein, crude fiber and other components ( Sun and Liu, 1993)
